{"tid":584384,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［公投］生命到底係點嚟？","createTime":"2018-03-07T19:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T09:16:54.000Z","uid":149844,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8ff24b4961586bd8e86d9dd291ae77677899d169","tid":584384,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T19:16:15.000Z","msg":"相信每個人都有諗過自己係點樣嚟到依個世界？<br />\n但係通常得到嘅答案都係老豆老媽扑野生你出嚟<br />\n其實世界點止咁簡單，當你一直追溯到生命嘅源頭<br />\n你會問第一個男人同女人係點嚟？<br />\n再問到第一隻雞第一隻狗點嚟？<br />\n就基本上無人可以好確定咁答到你<br />\n想簡單做個投票<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  =達爾文進化論 物種進化與淘汰（無神論）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =愛因斯坦相對論 星塵由上帝按排好（有神論）"},{"pid":"7d7a8867f80717dc9b33413336e1c146077eb005","tid":584384,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T19:41:05.000Z","msg":"巧合."},{"pid":"231cdefde7cb80bae6bdf4b48e14236cf86fedda","tid":584384,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:16:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"424b501ab5fd19e1b468e16534d695166ffb9e9a","tid":584384,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:16:54.000Z","msg":"參考資料<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/9/11/3/n2709557.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F9%2F11%2F3%2Fn2709557.htm&d=mxLN5WoiqLJ7Y%2BmPCDGGnQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=55ae25cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.epochtimes.com/b5/9/11/3/n2709557.htm</a>"}]}